{"ID":"20260305082130-32f4jyd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-32f4jyd","title":"友元","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-c1w0jsv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-c1w0jsv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 什么是友元？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-m10xpin","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-m10xpin","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 C++ 中，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"友元 (Friend)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 是一种特殊的机制，它允许一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"非成员函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"另一个类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，或者"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"另一个类的特定成员函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，访问声明它为友元的类的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"private"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"protected"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 成员。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-9tffdhz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9tffdhz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"友元是 C++ 封装原则的一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"受控的例外"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它允许你选择性地“打破”封装，为特定的外部实体提供对类内部实现的访问权限。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-w9ng1cl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-w9ng1cl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 如何声明友元？"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-t97wxd1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-t97wxd1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"友元通过在类定义内部使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"friend"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 关键字来声明。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-aq7a6b7","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-aq7a6b7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-iaw0hp7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-iaw0hp7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-uz5luzb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uz5luzb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"友元函数 (Friend Function)"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"非成员函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明为友元。这个函数可以是全局函数，也可以是另一个类的成员函数（但不是当前类的成员函数）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sgnmhmr","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockFenceOffset":2,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sgnmhmr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \u003ciostream\u003e\n\nclass MyClass {\nprivate:\n    int privateData;\npublic:\n    MyClass(int data) : privateData(data) {}\n    // 声明一个全局函数 printPrivateData 为 MyClass 的友元\n    friend void printPrivateData(const MyClass\u0026 obj);\n};\n\n// 友元函数的定义 (它不是 MyClass 的成员函数)\nvoid printPrivateData(const MyClass\u0026 obj) {\n    // 作为友元，它可以访问 MyClass 的私有成员\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Friend Function: Accessing privateData = \" \u003c\u003c obj.privateData \u003c\u003c std::endl;\n}\n\n// int main() {\n//     MyClass obj(10);\n//     printPrivateData(obj); // 输出: Friend Function: Accessing privateData = 10\n//     return 0;\n// }\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-oocky0h","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-oocky0h","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-258g0tr","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-258g0tr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-im2fvh3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-im2fvh3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"友元类 (Friend Class)"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"另一个类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明为友元。被声明为友元的类中的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"所有成员函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"都可以访问声明友元类的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"private"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"protected"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 成员。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hu2vgjq","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockFenceOffset":2,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hu2vgjq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 需要前向声明 OtherClass，因为 MyClass 在定义 OtherClass 之前就引用了它\n\nclass OtherClass;\nclass MyClass {\nprivate:\n    int privateData;\npublic:\n    MyClass(int data) : privateData(data) {}\n    // 声明 OtherClass 为 MyClass 的友元\n    friend class OtherClass;\n};\n\nclass OtherClass {\npublic:\n    void accessMyClassPrivate(const MyClass\u0026 obj) {\n        // 作为友元类，OtherClass 的成员函数可以访问 MyClass 的私有成员\n        std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Friend Class: OtherClass accessing privateData = \" \n  \t\t\u003c\u003c obj.privateData \u003c\u003c std::endl;\n    }\n    void anotherOtherFunction(const MyClass\u0026 obj) {\n        // 这个函数也是 OtherClass 的成员，所以也能访问 MyClass 的私有成员\n        std::cout \n          \u003c\u003c \"Friend Class: Another OtherClass function accessing privateData = \" \n          \u003c\u003c obj.privateData \u003c\u003c std::endl;\n    }\n};\n\n// int main() {\n//     MyClass obj(20);\n//     OtherClass otherObj;\n//     otherObj.accessMyClassPrivate(obj); // 输出: Friend Class: OtherClass accessing privateData = 20\n//     otherObj.anotherOtherFunction(obj); // 输出: Friend Class: Another OtherClass function accessing privateData = 20\n//     return 0;\n// }\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-giqeqsy","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-giqeqsy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-pulhivd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pulhivd","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-beirsep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-beirsep","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"友元成员函数 (Friend Member Function)"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"另一个类的特定成员函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"声明为友元。这是最精细的友元控制方式，只有被声明的那个成员函数才能访问私有和保护成员。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1thtoqw","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockFenceOffset":2,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1thtoqw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 需要前向声明 OtherClass\nclass OtherClass;\nclass MyClass {\nprivate:\n    int privateData;\npublic:\n    MyClass(int data) : privateData(data) {}\n    // 声明 OtherClass 的某个成员函数 accessMyClassPrivate 为 MyClass 的友元\n    friend void OtherClass::accessMyClassPrivate(const MyClass\u0026 obj);\n};\n\nclass OtherClass {\npublic:\n    void accessMyClassPrivate(const MyClass\u0026 obj) {\n        // 作为友元成员函数，它可以访问 MyClass 的私有成员\n        std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Friend Member Function: OtherClass::accessMyClassPrivate accessing privateData = \" \n          \u003c\u003c obj.privateData \u003c\u003c std::endl;\n    }\n    void anotherOtherFunction(const MyClass\u0026 obj) {\n        // 这个函数不是友元，所以不能访问 MyClass 的私有成员\n        // std::cout \u003c\u003c obj.privateData \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 错误：'int MyClass::privateData' is private\n    }\n};\n\n// int main() {\n//     MyClass obj(30);\n//     OtherClass otherObj;\n//     otherObj.accessMyClassPrivate(obj); // 输出: Friend Member Function: OtherClass::accessMyClassPrivate accessing privateData = 30\n//     otherObj.anotherOtherFunction(obj); // 编译错误\n//     return 0;\n// }\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-bqmsye3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bqmsye3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 友元的作用和目的"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-bwak30o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bwak30o","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"友元的主要作用是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提供受控的访问权限，以实现特定的设计需求"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它在以下场景中特别有用："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-e3rlmfy","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-e3rlmfy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-y9ju8ud","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y9ju8ud","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-6jlhkz4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-6jlhkz4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"运算符重载 (Operator Overloading)："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-wa2e0n2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wa2e0n2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ 这是友元最常见的用途之一，尤其对于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"二元运算符"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（如 +, -, ）和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"流插入/提取运算符"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (\u003c\u003c, \u003e\u003e)。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ziqjtim","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ziqjtim","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ 当运算符的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"左侧操作数不是类的对象"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时（例如 std::cout \u003c\u003c myObject;），或者当运算符需要"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"对称地访问两个操作数的私有成员"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时，友元函数是必要的。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-21qp9kt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-21qp9kt","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"优势："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 允许隐式类型转换，使得自定义类型与内置类型的操作行为更一致。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-77lgehg","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-77lgehg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-enml6lk","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-enml6lk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-p8a72zm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-p8a72zm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"辅助函数 (Helper Functions)："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-7m0tfjq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-7m0tfjq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ 当一个函数与某个类紧密相关，需要访问其私有成员，但从语义上讲，它不适合作为该类的成员函数时，可以将其声明为友元。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-vgov2uj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vgov2uj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 一个用于打印类内部所有私有状态的调试函数。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-30apk3k","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-30apk3k","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-1ltfcpb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1ltfcpb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-z1ngrpk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-z1ngrpk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"相关类之间的紧密协作 (Closely Related Classes)："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-z93nc65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-z93nc65","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ 在某些情况下，两个类之间存在非常紧密的逻辑关系，以至于它们需要频繁且深入地访问彼此的私有成员。例如，一个容器类（如 LinkedList）可能需要直接操作其节点类（Node）的私有指针。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-j8an2ll","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-j8an2ll","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"优势："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 友元可以简化代码并提高效率，避免通过大量的公共 getter/setter 方法来间接访问。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-vlxsl19","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vlxsl19","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vurseug","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vurseug","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-u8q8c5m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u8q8c5m","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"迭代器 (Iterators)："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-9u6kxnu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9u6kxnu","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"▪ 迭代器通常需要访问它们所遍历的容器的私有数据，但它们本身不是容器的成员。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1azf6qg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1azf6qg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 友元的缺点和注意事项**"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-s9ymogb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-s9ymogb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽管友元提供了灵活性，但它也带来了一些潜在的问题，因此应该"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"谨慎使用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fsqtu4z","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fsqtu4z","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-wx63uf8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wx63uf8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-z3t2rki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-z3t2rki","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"破坏封装性："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 友元是封装原则的“后门”。过度使用友元会导致代码的耦合度增加，使得类内部的实现细节暴露给外部，降低了代码的可维护性和可扩展性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ifkib01","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ifkib01","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-p5o3yfc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-p5o3yfc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"增加复杂性："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 友元使得类的接口不再仅仅由其公共成员定义，还需要考虑友元函数或友元类，增加了理解和维护的难度。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-otah3sm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-otah3sm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-kk44uzv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-kk44uzv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"单向性："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 友元关系是单向的。如果 A 是 B 的友元，不意味着 B 也是 A 的友元。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-uaale32","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uaale32","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vqnk856","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vqnk856","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不继承："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 友元关系不能被继承。如果基类声明了友元，其派生类不会自动成为友元。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-egzula2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"5.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":5,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-egzula2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-0g6skhl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-0g6skhl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不传递："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 友元关系不具有传递性。如果 A 是 B 的友元，B 是 C 的友元，不意味着 A 是 C 的友元。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cqa4gx1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cqa4gx1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最佳实践："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-h9nuje4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-h9nuje4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"• "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"优先使用公共接口："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 总是优先考虑通过类的公共接口（公共成员函数，如 getter/setter）来访问私有数据。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sz2b2wi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sz2b2wi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"• "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最小化友元范围："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 如果确实需要友元，应尽可能使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"友元成员函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，而不是整个友元类，以最小化对封装的破坏。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1pxiqgw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1pxiqgw","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"• "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"仅在必要时使用："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 只有在没有更好的替代方案，且友元能显著简化设计或提高性能时才考虑使用。"}]}]}